\v 13 \w So|strong="H5921"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* stationed \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* lower places \w behind|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w wall|strong="H2346"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* exposed places. \w I|strong="H5921"\w* stationed \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w by|strong="H5921"\w* families, \w with|strong="H5921"\w* \w their|strong="H5921"\w* swords, spears, \w and|strong="H5971"\w* bows.
